  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f  \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Archaeological officials visited the Presidential Palace",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the officials had gone there to monitor whether there was any damage to the archaeological objects found there.",
        "During this, it is also reported that the officials of the Department of Archeology are planning to have a conversation with the youth staying at the Presidential Palace.",
        "Meanwhile, while many people from different parts of the country are coming to visit the President's House, which was seized by the demonstrators on the 9th, there have been reports that valuable items have been damaged and some valuable items have gone missing."
